'HYPOTENUSE FRACTION' CALCULATES THEHYPOTENUSE OF A RIGHT TRIANGLE INFEET AND FRACTIONS OF INCHES.IN RESPONSE TO THE PROMPT; ENTER THENUMBER OF FEET; NUMBER OF WHOLEINCHES; THE NUMERATOR FOR THEFRACTION OF INCHES; AND THEDENOMINATOR. FOR EXAMPLE; IF ONESIDE OF THE TRIANGLE IS6 FEET; 5 3/4 INCHES; YOU WOULDENTER 6;5;3;4 IN RESPONSE TO THEPROMPT.THE ANSWER WILL ALSO BE GIVEN INTHESE UNITS.